# Trivy ignore file — JATIC SDP DSOR-1-H-3 / CS-2-H-2
#
# Per-finding CVE suppressions consumed by `scan:docker` in .gitlab-ci.yml.
# Every entry MUST follow the format below. Suppressions without all three
# header lines will be rejected at code review (see SECURITY.md).
#
#     # Justification: <one-line reason why this CVE is not exploitable here>
#     # Upstream:      <link to upstream advisory / patch> or "no fix yet"
#     # Re-evaluate:   YYYY-MM-DD  (90d for HIGH/CRITICAL, 180d for MEDIUM)
#     CVE-YYYY-NNNNN
#
# When the re-evaluation date passes, the suppression must be removed or
# re-justified — there are no indefinite dismissals. Active suppressions are
# audited at each release cut per BRANCHING.md.
#
# (no active suppressions)
